Note about the firmware binaries (firmware/*.bin)
================================================================

The binary firmware images distributed in this repository are compiled
from a separate source repository (private). These binaries statically
link against several open-source libraries (Arduino-ESP32, RadioLib,
ArduinoJson, Adafruit sensor drivers, etc.), each with their own license.

The binaries are provided here for convenience of users wishing to flash
the LoRa-LTE Node hardware. Attributions and source code for the embedded
libraries are available through their respective upstream projects.

